==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|es}}

#{{computing}} A device, in which one or a combination of [[key]]s are pressed to [[punch]] [[hole]]s in [[punched card]]s or [[paper tape]] that correspond to a particular [[character]]
#{{computing}} an [[electric]] machine with a [[keyboard]] that has the same function

===Verb===
'''to keypunch'''

# To use such a device or machine

